TEXT.S:
Almazbek Atambayev u ngangan nu Hulam: ·
u siwkay niza 9 bulad 17 demiad, Almazbek Atambayev, u misingkiway. 1956 a mihca nalecuhan. u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Kazakhstanayza sa ci Almazbek Atambayev, micakat a demiad sa i 2011 a mihca 12 bulad 1 demiad. u kulit nu hata nu Kazakhstan situsa a kulit, u sumanahay atu takuliway.
kakuniza u nasulitan nu Hulam atu Amilika · Almazbek Sharshenovich Atambayev has been the President of Kyrgyzstan since 1 December 2011. He was Prime Minister of Kyrgyzstan from 17 December 2010 to 1 December 2011, and from 29 March 2007 to 28 November 2007. He served as Chairman of the Social Democratic Party of Kyrgyzstan (SDPK) from 30 July 1999 to 23 September 2011.
